room_title: Escape room "Swindler's List" by Maggie Valley Puzzle Rooms in Maggie Valley
review: We had so much fun losing in the Swindler's Room! We enjoyed the puzzles & the teamwork. The hour just flew by. We were very close, but did not make it out in time. We all agreed that it was an hour well spent. Everyone contributed to solving the puzzles and the hints were extremely helpful. I would do this again in a heartbeat!
